{"tid":1814954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大民調：近八成市民指今屆區選公平公正","createTime":"2020-01-07T07:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:08:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6da6caeded943a6ba5fcdee8e6a9d1a10bb304bb","tid":1814954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"中大亞太研究所公布一項針對今屆區議會選舉看法，結果顯示78.9%受訪市民認為今屆區議會選舉是「公平公正」，當中51.4%回答「同意」、27.5%回答非常同意。<br />\n<br />\n中大香港亞太研究所於去年12月16日至20日進行電話訪問調查，結果顯示，在有投票的登記選民中，50.5%表示近期反修例事件有影響他們的投票選擇，47.2%表示沒有受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n調查又指出，投票給非建制派候選人的受訪者，較受到近期反對修例運動影響，相關比率有55.8%，另外，有18%受訪者表示自己是第一次在區議會選舉中投票，非首次投票的則有82%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2348117/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2348117%2F&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=02f4add7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2348117/</a>"},{"pid":"ae4b33af054dee9c4ffbce98bd52e1b9fdb0e7e0","tid":1814954,"uid":316751,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"一啲都唔公平喎，有咩理由親共派仲有席位"},{"pid":"ae6017a49fb48460181f185dcdde21efc44e4a6b","tid":1814954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995b12549545f049fdb66f92b002f53bcf4d757e","tid":1814954,"uid":7125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"雖然大勝唔代表公平公正<br />\n<br />\n種票買票做數做到痴晒線 去到立法會唔係單議席單配制就大鑊了"},{"pid":"857447a9726f3b7e4444c0a6f6f2ab2ac42caf57","tid":1814954,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"其實唔公平，我哋贏係我哋勁。"},{"pid":"49d1771ae6f1eee3ed3c3a11904be38e7091e7aa","tid":1814954,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:29:06.000Z","msg":"有8區有問題<br